Package: skpr
Title: skpr
Version: 0.13.3.0
Authors@R: c(person("Tyler", "Morgan-Wall", email = "tmorganw@ida.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("George", "Khoury", email = "george.m.khoury@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: Generates optimal designs and calculates power for those designs given a model and a factorial design for the given parameters. Evaluation can be done with both normal approximation techniques and Monte Carlo methods, and includes a method to evaluate a censored response variable. A parallel implementation of the Monte Carlo method is also provided.
Depends:
  doParallel,
  foreach,
  survival
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports:
  nlme,
  lme4,
  RcppArmadillo,
  Rcpp (>= 0.11.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: testthat
